channel.title: [659]Uncalled Attack - The Best Ever
channel.description:
[center][img]http://img97.imageshack.us/img97/5683/uabanner1c.jpg[/img][/center] Q: [i]Uncalled, didn't you quit?[/i] A: [i]Yes, still won't be on Mopar, but while I was here I might as well tell you I'm still working on something.[/i]
[b]Want to beta test? Click the link in my signature to play it![/b]
Hello guys, another project that I'm going to [b]rape[/b], :) with your support. We have the hitsplats added, 659 items, objects, maps, etc. I don't have a webclient due to the fact I'm most-likely not going to host this, I will have it webclient ready before I release it to you guys, if you choose [on the poll] that you want me to release it. I might release this; that's completely up to you guys though. I want to tell you that the Uncalled Attack projects aren't going to die off, this topic will pretty much prove that fact. This is my 2nd time working with a source that's deob is higher than 600, so it might not be that great.
[b]update Log:[/b] [code]Sept. 04: I messed with Combat a lil, raised the meele def multipler, so nothing will be overpowered since the defence is being multiplied higher. Sept. 04; Updated combat, range and magic, still not perfect. -Uncalled Sept. 04; Updated ranging, still not perfect. -Uncalled Sept. 04; Updated thieving -imsuperman05 Sept. 04; Fixed the thieving xp glitch. -Uncalled Sept. 05; Added voting rewards, the ::reward command isn't working though. -Uncalled Sett. 06; Fixed up some alching and mining. -pk2play Sept. 07: Fixed the alching the saradomin sword to 9m instead of 55m. Sept. 07: Added a better CharacterDesign class, so we can make a makeover mage. -pk2play[/code] [hr] We're already gaining a community! [img]http://img51.imageshack.us/img51/1035/uacom.png[/img] [hr] Here's a video: [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rIw6fKpQo8s[/youtube] [hr] Here's a few little pictures: [img]http://img856.imageshack.us/img856/320/ua6571.png[/img] [img]http://img62.imageshack.us/img62/1568/ua6572.png[/img] [img]http://img717.imageshack.us/img717/1351/ua6573.png[/img] [img]http://img851.imageshack.us/img851/4498/ua6574.png[/img] [img]http://img38.imageshack.us/img38/2920/ua6575.png[/img] [img]http://img708.imageshack.us/img708/7687/ua6576.png[/img] [img]http://img228.imageshack.us/img228/9223/ua6577.png[/img] [img]http://img263.imageshack.us/img263/6287/ua6578.png[/img] [img]http://img221.imageshack.us/img221/1953/ua6579.png[/img] [img]http://img29.imageshack.us/img29/7342/ua65710.png[/img] [img]http://img831.imageshack.us/img831/3339/ua65711.png[/img][img]http://img827.imageshack.us/img827/2561/ua65712.png[/img] [img]http://img508.imageshack.us/img508/7420/ua65713.png[/img][img]http://img828.imageshack.us/img828/968/ua65714.png[/img] [img]http://img847.imageshack.us/img847/8663/ua65715.png[/img] [img]http://img217.imageshack.us/img217/6540/ua65718.png[/img] [img]http://img840.imageshack.us/img840/5223/ua65719.png[/img] [img]http://img638.imageshack.us/img638/9193/ua65720.png[/img] [img]http://img268.imageshack.us/img268/8990/ua65721.png[/img] [img]http://img705.imageshack.us/img705/2203/ua65722.png[/img] [img]http://img42.imageshack.us/img42/9994/ua65723.png[/img] [img]http://img607.imageshack.us/img607/5319/ua65724.png[/img] [img]http://img28.imageshack.us/img28/9444/ua65726.png[/img] [img]http://img20.imageshack.us/img20/4580/ua65727.png[/img] [img]http://img405.imageshack.us/img405/5747/ua65728.png[/img] [img]http://img217.imageshack.us/img217/8148/ua65733.png[/img] [img]http://img217.imageshack.us/img217/5360/ua65730.png[/img] [img]http://img196.imageshack.us/img196/1864/ua65732.png[/img] More will come soon when I add more.
